lines.text: [closing scenery after the owner discovers the 4 kittens of Butch, he ran out the door to try hide them]

[after the owner chases Butch & sees the 4 look alike kittens]
Oh, they're adorable. And they look just like you, Butch. They're chips off the old block.

[last line, just before closing credits Butch also sounds like Donald Duck]
Well, I'll be doggone.
